Hi all,
Can anyone help with outputting dynamic quote values in the quote template?

I've created a custom module and also duplicated the HubSpot default quote template to which I've included this custom module, now when I want to output quote value &amp; currency dynamically to each quote it doesn't want to show.

I created quote fields which pull from quote objects (see screenshot) but anytime I try and create a new quote and I publish it and preview it I can see those details.

These are variables I'm using.

&lt;p&gt;Currency: {{ module.quote_object.properties.hs_currency }}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amount: {{ module.quote_object.properties.hs_quote_amount }}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Quote ID: {{ module.quote_object.properties.hs_quote_number }}&lt;/p&gt;
